            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ENever%20has%20there%20been%20an%20illustration%20of%20a%20people%20more%20excited%20and%20generous%20toward%20fulfilling%20a%20vision%20than%20that%20of%20the%20Israelites%20giving%20toward%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20tabernacle%20in%20the%20wilderness.%20The%20Israelites%20were%20so%20grateful%20to%20God%20for%20delivering%20them%20from%20Egypt%20that%20they%20delighted%20to%20give%20of%20their%20wealth%20and%20labor%20to%20build%20a%20magnificent%20sanctuary.%20Loaded%20with%20the%20silver%2C%20gold%2C%20and%20jewels%20that%20the%20Egyptians%20had%20given%20them%20the%20night%20of%20their%20departure%2C%20they%20willingly%20set%20their%20hearts%20to%20work%2C%20sew%2C%20and%20build.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Israelites'%20example%20characterizes%20the%20power%20of%20the%20church%20when%20united%20by%20a%20common%20vision.%20Why%20not%20catch%20the%20vision%20of%20your%20church%20and%20apply%20your%20full%20strength%20and%20resources%20toward%20making%20that%20vision%20a%20reality%3F%20What%20has%20God%20given%20you%3F%20A%20talent%3F%20Some%20unexpected%20income%3F%20Some%20extra%20time%3F%20Find%20the%20vision%20God%20is%20building%20in%20you%20and%20your%20church%20and%20then%20work%20with%20your%20whole%20soul%20toward%20achieving%20it%20until%20you%20have%20to%20be%20told%2C%20%22Enough!%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%20gave%20His%20all%20on%20the%20cross.%20He%20withheld%20nothing.%20The%20least%20you%20can%20do%20is%20to%20give%20bountifully%20of%20the%20resources%20His%20death%20secured%20for%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
