            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EExodus%2035%3A10-36%3A38%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_10%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BCome%2C%20all%20of%20you%20who%20are%20gifted%20craftsmen.%20Construct%20everything%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20commanded%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_11%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20Tabernacle%20and%20its%20sacred%20tent%2C%20its%20covering%2C%20clasps%2C%20frames%2C%20crossbars%2C%20posts%2C%20and%20bases%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_12%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20Ark%20and%20its%20carrying%20poles%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20Ark%26%23x2019%3Bs%20cover%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20place%20of%20atonement%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20inner%20curtain%20to%20shield%20the%20Ark%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_13%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20table%2C%20its%20carrying%20poles%2C%20and%20all%20its%20utensils%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20Bread%20of%20the%20Presence%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_14%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Efor%20light%2C%20the%20lampstand%2C%20its%20accessories%2C%20the%20lamp%20cups%2C%20and%20the%20olive%20oil%20for%20lighting%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_15%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20incense%20altar%20and%20its%20carrying%20poles%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20anointing%20oil%20and%20fragrant%20incense%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20curtain%20for%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_16%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20altar%20of%20burnt%20offering%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20bronze%20grating%20of%20the%20altar%20and%20its%20carrying%20poles%20and%20utensils%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20washbasin%20with%20its%20stand%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_17%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20curtains%20for%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20courtyard%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20posts%20and%20their%20bases%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list%22%3Ethe%20curtain%20for%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20courtyard%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_18%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20tent%20pegs%20of%20the%20Tabernacle%20and%20courtyard%20and%20their%20ropes%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_19%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22list-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20beautifully%20stitched%20garments%20for%20the%20priests%20to%20wear%20while%20ministering%20in%20the%20Holy%20Place%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20sacred%20garments%20for%20Aaron%20the%20priest%2C%20and%20the%20garments%20for%20his%20sons%20to%20wear%20as%20they%20minister%20as%20priests.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_20%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20whole%20community%20of%20Israel%20left%20Moses%20and%20returned%20to%20their%20tents.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_21%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20whose%20hearts%20were%20stirred%20and%20whose%20spirits%20were%20moved%20came%20and%20brought%20their%20sacred%20offerings%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20They%20brought%20all%20the%20materials%20needed%20for%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E35%3A21%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ETent%20of%20Meeting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20the%20performance%20of%20its%20rituals%2C%20and%20for%20the%20sacred%20garments.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_22%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EBoth%20men%20and%20women%20came%2C%20all%20whose%20hearts%20were%20willing.%20They%20brought%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20their%20offerings%20of%20gold%26%23x2014%3Bbrooches%2C%20earrings%2C%20rings%20from%20their%20fingers%2C%20and%20necklaces.%20They%20presented%20gold%20objects%20of%20every%20kind%20as%20a%20special%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_23%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20those%20who%20owned%20the%20following%20items%20willingly%20brought%20them%3A%20blue%2C%20purple%2C%20and%20scarlet%20thread%3B%20fine%20linen%20and%20goat%20hair%20for%20cloth%3B%20and%20tanned%20ram%20skins%20and%20fine%20goatskin%20leather.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_24%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20all%20who%20had%20silver%20and%20bronze%20objects%20gave%20them%20as%20a%20sacred%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20And%20those%20who%20had%20acacia%20wood%20brought%20it%20for%20use%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_25%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20the%20women%20who%20were%20skilled%20in%20sewing%20and%20spinning%20prepared%20blue%2C%20purple%2C%20and%20scarlet%20thread%2C%20and%20fine%20linen%20cloth.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_26%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20the%20women%20who%20were%20willing%20used%20their%20skills%20to%20spin%20the%20goat%20hair%20into%20yarn.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_27%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20leaders%20brought%20onyx%20stones%20and%20the%20special%20gemstones%20to%20be%20set%20in%20the%20ephod%20and%20the%20priest%26%23x2019%3Bs%20chestpiece.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_28%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20also%20brought%20spices%20and%20olive%20oil%20for%20the%20light%2C%20the%20anointing%20oil%2C%20and%20the%20fragrant%20incense.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_29%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%26%23x2014%3Bevery%20man%20and%20woman%20who%20was%20eager%20to%20help%20in%20the%20work%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20given%20them%20through%20Moses%26%23x2014%3Bbrought%20their%20gifts%20and%20gave%20them%20freely%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_30%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20told%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20specifically%20chosen%20Bezalel%20son%20of%20Uri%2C%20grandson%20of%20Hur%2C%20of%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_31%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20filled%20Bezalel%20with%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%2C%20giving%20him%20great%20wisdom%2C%20ability%2C%20and%20expertise%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20crafts.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_32%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20a%20master%20craftsman%2C%20expert%20in%20working%20with%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20bronze.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_33%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20skilled%20in%20engraving%20and%20mounting%20gemstones%20and%20in%20carving%20wood.%20He%20is%20a%20master%20at%20every%20craft.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_34%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20given%20both%20him%20and%20Oholiab%20son%20of%20Ahisamach%2C%20of%20the%20tribe%20of%20Dan%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20teach%20their%20skills%20to%20others.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_35_35%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20given%20them%20special%20skills%20as%20engravers%2C%20designers%2C%20embroiderers%20in%20blue%2C%20purple%2C%20and%20scarlet%20thread%20on%20fine%20linen%20cloth%2C%20and%20weavers.%20They%20excel%20as%20craftsmen%20and%20as%20designers.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_36_1%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EExodus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20gifted%20Bezalel%2C%20Oholiab%2C%20and%20the%20other%20skilled%20craftsmen%20with%20wisdom%20and%20ability%20to%20perform%20any%20task%20involved%20in%20building%20the%20sanctuary.%20Let%20them%20construct%20and%20furnish%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20commanded.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_36_2%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Moses%20summoned%20Bezalel%20and%20Oholiab%20and%20all%20the%20others%20who%20were%20specially%20gifted%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20were%20eager%20to%20get%20to%20work.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_36_3%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EMoses%20gave%20them%20the%20materials%20donated%